    "Required input parameters (must be present in your workflow JSON):",
    "  - image_path  (LoadImage node — path to keyframe PNG from executor_keyframe)",
    "  - motion_prompt (text node — motion description from shotlist)",
    "  - num_frames  (compute from duration_s * fps, e.g. 2.5s * 24 = 60 frames)",
    "  - fps         (default 24)",
    "",
    "Required output: SaveVideo node producing MP4",
    "",
